{{!-- subject --}}
{{inviterName}} shared "{{noteTitle}}" with you on Notesaner
{{!-- /subject --}}

{{!-- html --}}
<h1>A note has been shared with you</h1>
<p>Hi {{displayName}},</p>
<p><strong>{{inviterName}}</strong> has shared the note <strong>{{noteTitle}}</strong> with you{{#if workspaceName}} from the workspace <strong>{{workspaceName}}</strong>{{/if}}.</p>
{{#if message}}
<blockquote style="border-left: 3px solid #5b50f0; margin: 16px 0; padding: 8px 16px; background: #f8f7ff; border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;">
  <p style="margin: 0; font-style: italic;">{{message}}</p>
</blockquote>
{{/if}}
<a href="{{{noteUrl}}}" class="btn">Open note</a>
<hr class="divider" />
<p class="muted">You can view this note with {{permission}} access. If you were not expecting this invitation, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
{{!-- /html --}}

{{!-- text --}}
{{inviterName}} shared "{{noteTitle}}" with you on Notesaner

Hi {{displayName}},

{{inviterName}} has shared the note "{{noteTitle}}" with you{{#if workspaceName}} from the workspace "{{workspaceName}}"{{/if}}.
{{#if message}}
Message from {{inviterName}}:
  "{{message}}"
{{/if}}
Open note: {{{noteUrl}}}

You can view this note with {{permission}} access.

— The Notesaner team
{{!-- /text --}}
